if your project already uses peal then
1) add palmpng.ro to your prcfile (combine it)
2) add to your 68k project files from src-m68k, only files, not symlinked files
3) include palmpng.h to your project where you need it


if your project doesn't use peal
1) add palmpng.ro to your prcfile (combine it)
2) add to your 68k project library palmpng.a
3) include palmpng.h to your project where you need it

rest of usage comments is described in palmpng.h

for png optimizer take a look into src-pngopt directory
you will have to co pile it for your system and it will need libpng and libz installed
(including headers, usualy in packages with -dev suffix)
